Privacy Policy


1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how SJI Prayer Times (“the App”) collects, uses, and protects user information.
We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it.

2. Information We Collect

a) Location Information

The App may request access to your device’s location (GPS) to:

Automatically determine your current city
Calculate accurate prayer times based on your location

Note: Location access is optional
You may deny location permission and manually select a location instead.

We do not store, track, or share your precise location.

b) Personal Information

The App does not collect any personally identifiable information such as:

Name
Email address
Phone number
Account credentials
No login or account creation is required.

c) Device Information

The App does not collect device identifiers, advertising IDs, or analytics data.

3. How We Use Information

Any information used by the App is processed locally on your device and is used only to:
Calculate prayer times
Display Islamic dates and times
Improve accuracy based on user-selected settings
No data is transmitted to external servers.

4. Data Sharing

We do not share any data with:

Third parties
Advertisers
Analytics providers
Government or private entities

5. Data Storage and Security

All settings (such as prayer calculation method or Hijri offset) are stored locally on your device
No user data is uploaded or backed up to external servers

6. Children’s Privacy

The App is suitable for all age groups.
We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children.

7. Permissions Explanation

The App may request the following permission:

Location (ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION / ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION)
Used only to calculate accurate prayer times based on your location.

This permission is optional and can be revoked at any time from device settings.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.
Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated effective date.




